Maabaho kanilongela, "Sekeuwase mbuli za ulotezi wa Mulungu zili muna ichitabu chino kwaviya lusita lwahabehi ng'hani.
Munhu yoyose yotenda yehile na yagendelele kutenda yehile, munhu yoyose yambule mwiko na yagendelele kutenda yehile, munhu yoyose yotenda yanogile haulongozi wa Mulungu na yagendelele kutenda yoyomnogeza Mulungu, munhu yelile na yagendelele kuwa yelile."
